description: Have you been craving a refreshing treat on the Utah streets? Then you won't find anything better than the authentic Hawaiian shave ice from Huli Boys! With all the fantastic flavors you'd find on the islands, you're sure to find something to love when you try this truck. This family run truck has the friendliest service and most refreshing frozen treats around, so don't miss out on Huli Boys!
name: Huli Boys
